data.description: Nestled in the highly sought-after Sierra Montana community of Surprise, this exquisite 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom residence boasts exceptional upgrades. Whole house water softener. Both AC units (5 ton each) were installed in 3/2023. Revel in the expansive formal dining room and living room, a separate den, and an extraordinary kitchen equipped with double ovens, a gas range, an expansive island, upgraded cabinetry featuring pull-out drawers, granite countertops, and an ample walk-in pantry complemented by a butler pantry. Ascend to the upper level to discover the luxurious master retreat, complete with a fireplace, sitting room, and a bonus room. The master bathroom showcases dual vanities and sinks, a soaking tub enveloped in upgraded tile surround, and a separate glass shower. Each bedroom and a separate glass shower. Each bedroom is accompanied by an attached bathroom, with two sharing a jack-n-jill bath and one possessing its own en suite. Step into the backyard oasis to relish the covered patio, pool featuring a water feature, and a built-in barbecue. Positioned adjacent to a green belt, this residence epitomizes a perfect blend of style and comfort.
